** Featured Tattoo: Watch the video below and please take a minute to read=
 Emmy=E2=80=99s inspiring interview.
------------------------------------------------------------
https://www.youtube.com/shorts/feGrTuI3lZk


** This is one of our favorites from 2025. We hope you=E2=80=99ll read Emm=
y=E2=80=99s emotional story and if you=E2=80=99re looking for a tattoo in=
 Ho Chi Minh City=2C visit Mr. Tien at Story Art Tattoo who created this b=
eautiful piece of art.
------------------------------------------------------------


** S.M.: Hi Emmy. While we now know your Soundwave Tattoo contains your mo=
m=E2=80=99s voice=2C what was it about this moment and her words that made=
 you want to keep it with you?
------------------------------------------------------------

Emmy (Translated from Vietnamese): =E2=80=9CWhen I recorded my mother's vo=
ice=2C she was still living with me and I simply thought I would give her=
 a surprising and meaningful birthday gift. I recorded my mother's voice i=
n 2019 when I accidentally saw a Soundwave Tattoo online and I thought it=
 was quite meaningful. My mother was a strong woman and my mother and I co=
uldn't easily share our feelings with each other. We had never said "I lov=
e you" to each other. By the time I got this dragonfly tattoo on my body=
=2C my mother had passed away forever; she died during the Covid-19 pandem=
ic in 2021. So the words in this recording are truly very meaningful to me=
; they encourage me whenever I feel weak=2C defeated=2C and want to give u=
p.=E2=80=9D


** S.M.: That was such a terrible time in history and we=E2=80=99re so sor=
ry for your loss. How do your memories of her relate to the decision to in=
corporate her voice into a Dragonfly?
------------------------------------------------------------

Emmy: =E2=80=9CThe dragonfly symbolizes my mother's soul=2C a way to remem=
ber her and to know that she is always by my side=2C even if not in the fo=
rm of a physical human being.

=E2=80=A2 A gentle soul is always present: not noisy=2C but a feeling that=
 my mother is still watching over me.

=E2=80=A2 Transformation and continuity: my mother is gone=2C but her love=
 and protection continue to exist within me.

=E2=80=A2 Presence without constraint: like a dragonfly =E2=80=93 flying t=
hrough my life=2C leaving a feeling of peace=2C not heavy loss.

=E2=80=A2 The image of a small=2C delicate=2C and subtly colored dragonfly=
=2C as if it is fading away (just like a soul flying towards the sky)=2C n=
ot too sharp =E2=86=92 a gentle feeling=2C like my mother's soul flying to=
 heaven.

=E2=80=A2 Only one dragonfly in the image =E2=86=92 like a private=2C unpr=
etentious feeling=2C like the image of me having only one mother in the wo=
rld.

This tattoo stems from love and gratitude; it's a beautiful way to say:=
 =E2=80=98I will always remember you=2C Mom=2C and I will continue to live=
 with all that you expected of me=2C and I will always remember your words=
: 'Ngan=2C keep going=2C I'm always by your side=2C keep trying=E2=80=99!=
=E2=80=9D


** S.M.: That is such an inspiration! And you trusted this very  emotional=
 tribute to a special tattoo artist who brought it to life. What can you t=
ell us about them?
------------------------------------------------------------

Emmy: =E2=80=9CI contacted Mr. Tien (Tymon Nguyen =E2=80=93 Story Art Tatt=
oo) in mid-2019 to inquire about a Soundwave Tattoo but it wasn't until 20=
20 that I had the opportunity to meet Mr. Tien in person to discuss and ha=
ve him design a Soundwave Tattoo for me. However=2C in 2020=2C the Covid p=
andemic hit=2C and my mother passed away during the pandemic=2C which was=
 a huge loss for me. Immediately afterward=2C I suffered from depression b=
ecause of this loss.=E2=80=9D

=E2=80=9CIn 2024 he contacted me again and informed me that he could now d=
o Soundwave Tattoos. And then in 2025=2C I finally got the dragonfly tatto=
o on my body. I am truly touched and grateful that after so many years=2C=
 Mr. Tien still remembers each of his clients and is so dedicated to every=
 tattoo he creates. Everyone around me who sees this tattoo praises its be=
auty and soulfulness=2C the beautiful and sharp color combination=2C and w=
hen they learn the meaning of the tattoo by scanning the image on the Skin=
motion app and hearing my story about my mother=2C they are all surprised=
=2C moved=2C and delighted.=E2=80=9D


** S.M.: We=E2=80=99re so appreciative that we could be a part of continui=
ng her memory. Thank you for sharing such an honest and emotional story. D=
ue to your love for her=2C your creativity and Mr. Tien=E2=80=99s phenomen=
al work=2C she continues to be an inspiration to so many around the world.
