ta-block-id=3D"22" class=3D"mceText" id=3D"d22" style=3D"width:100%"><h4 cl=
ass=3D"mcePastedContent"><span style=3D"font-size: 20px">This is one of our=
 favorites from 2025. We hope you=E2=80=99ll read Emmy=E2=80=99s emotional =
story and if you=E2=80=99re looking for a tattoo in Ho Chi Minh City, visit=
 Mr. Tien at Story Art Tattoo who created this beautiful piece of art. </sp=
an></h4><p><br></p><h4 class=3D"mcePastedContent"><span style=3D"font-size:=
 20px">S.M.: Hi Emmy. While we now know your Soundwave Tattoo contains your=
 mom=E2=80=99s voice, what was it about this moment and her words that made=
 you want to keep it with you?</span></h4><p><br></p><p class=3D"mcePastedC=
ontent"><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"font-size: 20px"=
>Emmy (Translated from Vietnamese): =E2=80=9CWhen I recorded my mother's vo=
ice, she was still living with me and I simply thought I would give her a s=
urprising and meaningful birthday gift. I recorded my mother's voice in 201=
9 when I accidentally saw a Soundwave Tattoo online and I thought it was qu=
ite meaningful. My mother was a strong woman and my mother and I couldn't e=
asily share our feelings with each other. We had never said &quot;I love yo=
u&quot; to each other. By the time I got this dragonfly tattoo on my body, =
my mother had passed away forever; she died during the Covid-19 pandemic in=
 2021. So the words in this recording are truly very meaningful to me; they=
 encourage me whenever I feel weak, defeated, and want to give up.=E2=80=9D=
</span></span></p><p class=3D"mcePastedContent"><br></p><p style=3D"line-he=
ight: 0; mso-line-height-alt: 0%;"><br></p><h4 class=3D"mcePastedContent"><=
span style=3D"font-size: 20px">S.M.: That was such a terrible time in histo=
ry and we=E2=80=99re so sorry for your loss. How do your memories of her re=
late to the decision to incorporate her voice into a Dragonfly?</span></h4>=
<p><br></p><p style=3D"line-height: 0; mso-line-height-alt: 0%;"><br></p><p=
 class=3D"mcePastedContent"><span style=3D"color:#000000;"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size: 20px">Emmy: =E2=80=9C</span></span><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0,=
 0);"><span style=3D"font-size: 20px">The dragonfly symbolizes my mother's =
soul, a way to remember her and to know that she is always by my side, even=
 if not in the form of a physical human being.</span></span></p><p><span st=
yle=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"font-size: 20px">=E2=80=A2 A gen=
tle soul is always present: not noisy, but a feeling that my mother is stil=
l watching over me.</span></span></p><p><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"=
><span style=3D"font-size: 20px">=E2=80=A2 Transformation and continuity: m=
y mother is gone, but her love and protection continue to exist within me.<=
/span></span></p><p><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"font=
-size: 20px">=E2=80=A2 Presence without constraint: like a dragonfly =E2=80=
=93 flying through my life, leaving a feeling of peace, not heavy loss.</sp=
an></span></p><p><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"font-si=
ze: 20px">=E2=80=A2 The image of a small, delicate, and subtly colored drag=
onfly, as if it is fading away (just like a soul flying towards the sky), n=
ot too sharp =E2=86=92 a gentle feeling, like my mother's soul flying to he=
aven.</span></span></p><p><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style=
=3D"font-size: 20px">=E2=80=A2 Only one dragonfly in the image =E2=86=92 li=
ke a private, unpretentious feeling, like the image of me having only one m=
other in the world.</span></span></p><p><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"=
><span style=3D"font-size: 20px">This tattoo stems from love and gratitude;=
 it's a beautiful way to say: =E2=80=98I will always remember you, Mom, and=
 I will continue to live with all that you expected of me, and I will alway=
s remember your words: 'Ngan, keep going, I'm always by your side, keep try=
ing=E2=80=99!=E2=80=9D</span></span></p><p><br></p><p style=3D"line-height:=
 0; mso-line-height-alt: 0%;"><br></p><h4 class=3D"mcePastedContent"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 20px">S.M.: That is such an inspiration! And you truste=
d this very &nbsp;emotional tribute to a special tattoo artist who brought =
it to life. </span><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"font-=
size: 20px">What can you tell us about them?</span></span></h4><p class=3D"=
mcePastedContent"><br></p><p><span style=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span styl=
e=3D"font-size: 20px">Emmy: =E2=80=9CI contacted Mr. Tien (Tymon Nguyen =E2=
=80=93 Story Art Tattoo) in mid-2019 to inquire about a Soundwave Tattoo bu=
t it wasn't until 2020 that I had the opportunity to meet Mr. Tien in perso=
n to discuss and have him design a Soundwave Tattoo for me. However, in 202=
0, the Covid pandemic hit, and my mother passed away during the pandemic, w=
hich was a huge loss for me. Immediately afterward, I suffered from depress=
ion because of this loss.=E2=80=9D</span></span></p><p><br></p><p><span sty=
le=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"font-size: 20px">=E2=80=9CIn 2024=
 he contacted me again and informed me that he could now do Soundwave Tatto=
os. And then in 2025, I finally got the dragonfly tattoo on my body. I am t=
ruly touched and grateful that after so many years, Mr. Tien still remember=
s each of his clients and is so dedicated to every tattoo he creates. Every=
one around me who sees this tattoo praises its beauty and soulfulness, the =
beautiful and sharp color combination, and when they learn the meaning of t=
he tattoo by scanning the image on the Skinmotion app and hearing my story =
about my mother, they are all surprised, moved, and delighted.=E2=80=9D</sp=
an></span></p><p><br></p><h4 class=3D"mcePastedContent last-child"><span st=
yle=3D"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"font-size: 20px">S.M.: We=E2=80=
=99re so appreciative that we could be a part of continuing her memory. Tha=
nk you for sharing such an honest and emotional story. Due to your love for=
 her, your creativity and Mr. Tien=E2=80=99s phenomenal work, she continues=
 to be an inspiration to so many around the world.</span></span></h4></div>=
